net.bytebuddy.dynamic.scaffold

Class TypeWriter.Default.ForInlining.FramePreservingRemapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • RemappingClassAdapter
      • net.bytebuddy.dynamic.scaffold.TypeWriter.Default.ForInlining.FramePreservingRemapper
  • Enclosing class:
    TypeWriter.Default.ForInlining<U>

    protected static class TypeWriter.Default.ForInlining.FramePreservingRemapper
extends RemappingClassAdapter
    A remapper adapter that does not attempt to reorder method frames which is never the case for a renaming. This adaption might not longer be necessary in the future: ASM #317576.
